# This is an example how to autotools can be used
# to deploy your C++ application

# All you need, call next commands

# aclocal && autoconf && automake --add-missing

OR

# autoreconf --install

to prepare configure script and Makefiles.
After that you can run

# ./configure

and

# make dist

command to get tarball to provide it for your users.

User just download tarball, unpack it and run ./configure && make && make install
commands